				<li id="16522199" class="cmnt-root" data="74" data-d="1647430594000"><ul class="comments"><li class="comment-box"><div class="avatar"><img src="/images/avatar.png" alt="" /><div class="comment-username">Anonymous</div></div><div class="comment"><div class="title"><span class="txt-subject"></span><input style="display: none;" class="txt-subject-ed"><span class="right cmt-ui"><a href="https://fextralife.com/forums/t576344/Reduvia" rel="nofollow" target="_blank">16 Mar 2022 07:36</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;<a class="report-post" href="https://fextralife.com/forums/report.php?f=193&p=16522199" rel="nofollow" target="_blank" title="report this post"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flag" aria-hidden="true"></span></a></span></div><p class="txt-comment">Short version: softcap for both on hit and skill shot bleed buildup is 50, second is 60.<br/>Long version. Arcane does affect bleed buildup of skill shots. Tested +6 Reduvia on big magic flowers vs. +15 Great Knife with ASH OF WAR: BLOOD BLADE. Numbers are for the FIRST proc, second requires +1-2 more shots for some reason.<br/>13 arcane: Reduvia - 6 shots to proc bleed, ash - 10, <br/>30 arcane: Reduvia - 5 shots to proc bleed, ash - 9, <br/>40 arcane: Reduvia - 5 shots to proc bleed, ash - 8, <br/>50 arcane: Reduvia - 4 shots to proc bleed, ash - 7, <br/>60 arcane: Reduvia - 4 shots to proc bleed, ash - 7, <br/>70 arcane: Reduvia - 4 shots to proc bleed, ash - 7, <br/>80 arcane: Reduvia - 4 shots to proc bleed, ash - 7, no point to test further.<br/>So bleed buildup from skills is affected by Arcane stat in the same way as on hit buildup. <br/>Arcane vs. on hit buildup on my +6 Reduvia:  <br/>30 -&gt; 40 = 62 -&gt; 75, <br/>40 -&gt; 50 = 75 -&gt; 82, <br/>50 -&gt; 60 = 82 -&gt; 86, <br/>60 -&gt; 70 = 82 -&gt; 87, <br/>70 -&gt; 80 = 82 -&gt; 88</p><textarea style="display: none;" class="txt-comment-ed"></textarea><div class="clearfix"><a role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#zz-16522199" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Reply</a><a id="btnExpandComment" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" href="#replies-16522199" class="cmt-reply pull-right" href=""><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-share-alt"></span>Replies (<span class="replies">2</span>)</a><div class="vote pull-right"><section class="t-up"><span></span><p>74</p><i class="add">+1</i></section><section class="t-down"><span></span><p>0</p><i class="sub">-1</i></section></div></div><div class="collapse-com transparent"><div class="col-trigger collapse" id="zz-16522199"><div class="ng-scope"><textarea id="dcomment" class="ng-pristine ng-untouched ng-invalid ng-invalid-required" placeholder="Input your comments:"></textarea><button id="btn-16522199" class="btn btn-default btnPostReply"><i class="glyphicon glyphicon-pencil"></i> Submit</button><img id="newCommentAvatar" src="/images/avatar.png"/></div></div></div></div><div class="clearfix"></div><ul class="children collapse" id="replies-16522199"></ul></li></ul></li>
			
